flow will be like
- user will connect woocommerce/shopify store with our platform
- when user replace order we will show order in our robocall dashboard
    - order will be in pending or in process (based on customization)
    - if in process bot will push call in queue
    - if pending show button to admin and admin will have to click on call button to push call in queue

Call bot:
- will check queue and call user phone number
- bot will confirm order status by user (by voice or keypad)
- once confirmed we will update order status to confirmed or cancelled based on user input
- we will call woocommerce/shopify api to update order status
- we will send notification to user (sms/email/push) about order status

- we will have retry mechanism if call fails or user does not respond
- we will have reporting dashboard to see call stats, order stats etc.
- we will have admin panel to customize call bots

Customization be like:
- like immediately calls or click on call button for call
- can change voice
- weither to use keypad or voice confirmation
    - for we will use simple twillio voice recognition
    - for voice recognition we will use gpt based voice recognition
        - user can provide its own apikey
        - or can use platform gpt apikey (will charge extra credits 0.5 credit per min of call)
- can change init lines and what he want to user to user initially

Subscription:
- we will have 2 types of subscription
    - credit based (1 call = 1 credit)
    - monthly package (unlimited calls per month)
- addons feature and provide 100 credits (if base on calls) or 7 days margin (if monthly package)

Settings
- basic auth settings (will update by time)




Technical details:
- when user place order we will use webhook to get order details and save in our supabase db
- in FE we will show order details on real-time using supabase real-time features